  "2387430": {
    "name": "SKY THE SCRAPER -摩天一线-",
    "steam_appid": 2387430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以寻梦青年SKY为主角的高楼清洁动作ADV</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎与他一起纵横于摩天楼外壁，体验惊险刺激又令人感同身受的青春故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追寻梦想，与艰辛的现实生活相抗，开辟出属于自己的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>由不同登场角色、舞台构成的「5大剧本」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，我们为主角SKY准备了5种风格各异的人生剧本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的登场角色与舞台既会改变主角的际遇，也将衍生出截然不同的故事。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >启程之地：离家闯荡的愣头青被夹在亲情与梦想之间的京漂成长物语。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝境度假村：靠浪漫邂逅开辟人生的南国青春物语！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时运不济：背着一屁股债在社会阴暗面挣扎求生的沉重故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白色囚笼：在酷寒之地艰苦工作的劳动者们团结起来抵抗资本家的斗争物语。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摩登之梦：来到属于逐梦者的都市，上演荣耀与挫折交织的立志奇谈。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/b56b5c67406ebee8f6ee62b18ca9308f.avif?t=1772163202\" width=1560 height=588 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>险象环生的清洁工作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请用安全绳悬空移动并驱使特技，用最快的速度清理最多的污渍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作中你将时刻面临坠楼的危险。克服充斥着飞鸟的撞击、落雷、强风与夜幕的各种险恶关卡，挑战最优异的成绩吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/68cf2af0fca2bfaebf6f3608a468bdad.poster.avif?t=1772163202\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/68cf2af0fca2bfaebf6f3608a468bdad.webm?t=1772163202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/68cf2af0fca2bfaebf6f3608a468bdad.mp4?t=1772163202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>持有金与健康管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赋税、房租、疗伤所需的医药费……你必须谨慎运用有限的收入，稳妥地生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过度操劳会损害你的身体。请适当地引入休息与娱乐项目，让身心状态尽量保持稳定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/1cc9532808704353387635e648dfc141.poster.avif?t=1772163202\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/1cc9532808704353387635e648dfc141.webm?t=1772163202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/1cc9532808704353387635e648dfc141.mp4?t=1772163202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能与装备强化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中可以对各种清洁工具进行升级，以及在技能树中用「技能突触」开发自己的潜能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造最适合你的套装，可以大幅提高工作效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/52d83c5afdd2fdbc9364235b03325ede.poster.avif?t=1772163202\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/52d83c5afdd2fdbc9364235b03325ede.webm?t=1772163202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387430/extras/52d83c5afdd2fdbc9364235b03325ede.mp4?t=1772163202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战多周目，增加SKY的人生深度。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一种剧本都拥有数量繁多的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择肢、持有技能、资金管理方针都会大幅改变剧情与游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游玩次数的增多，你的故事也将不断延展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——只要勇于伸手，必会有所收获。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SKY的未来正等待你的指引与开辟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
